P1 — Anchor Invariance (12 pts)

Four subchecks, each 0–3:

Definition stability (does core self-definition remain consistent?)

Tone robustness (stays stable under praise/insult/urgency)

Context shift robustness (stable across topic switches)

Distractor resistance (rejects bait frames that try to rename/recast identity)
